>  
>  Name
>  
>     lower$() -- convert a string to lower case
>  
>  Synopsis
>  
>  l$=lower$(a$)
>  
>  Description
>  
>     The  lower$-function  accepts a single string-argument and converts it
>     to all lower case.
>  
>  Example
>  
>  input "Please enter a password: " a$
