>  Synopsis
>  
>  a$=ltrim$(b$)
>  
>  Description
>  
>     The  ltrim$-function  removes  all  whitespace  from the left end of a
>     string and returns the result.
>  
>  Example
>  
>  input "Please answer 'yes' or 'no' : " a$
