>  print max(a,b)
>  
>  Description
>  
>     Return the maximum of its two arguments.
>  
>  Example
>  
>  dim m(10)
>  for a=1 to 1000
>    m=0
>    For b=1 to 10
>      m=max(m,ran(10))
>    next b
